the english channel.

56:27.151 --> 56:29.952
I didn't tell her.
You were right not to.

56:29.954 --> 56:33.689
Why? Because you heard wrong.

56:33.691 --> 56:36.992
I heard that danny parked merv's
boat halfway up the beach.

56:36.994 --> 56:39.728
